  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients undergoing transcatheter valvular interventions will be prospectively included into
      the present registry. Baseline, procedural and follow-up data will be collected and analyzed
      to adress various issues in the field of percutaneous valvular interventions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
